---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Dentures" 
  category="Tooth Replacement"
  description="Custom dentures made on-site with state-of-the-art fabrication equipment. Restore your smile and confidence with quality dentures."
  image="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3845553/pexels-photo-3845553.jpeg?auto=compress&w=800&h=600"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Restore Your Confidence</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Dentures are a removable plate or frame fitted to your mouth that hold one or more artificial teeth. 
        They are a replacement for missing teeth and they help to restore confidence in your smile. 
        We make dentures on site with state-of-the-art fabrication equipment.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Types of Dentures
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Complete Dentures -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Complete Dentures</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Replace all teeth in the upper or lower jaw. These rest on the gums and are held 
            in place by suction and dental adhesive.
          </p>
          
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Best For:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 text-sm">
            <li>• Patients missing all teeth in one or both jaws</li>
            <li>• Those seeking an affordable tooth replacement</li>
            <li>• Patients not suitable for implants</li>
            <li>• Immediate replacement after extractions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Partial Dentures -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-accent-200/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Partial Dentures</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Replace only some missing teeth while using your remaining natural teeth 
            as anchors for stability and retention.
          </p>
          
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Best For:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-600 text-sm">
            <li>• Patients with some healthy teeth remaining</li>
            <li>• Multiple missing teeth in different areas</li>
            <li>• Those wanting to preserve existing teeth</li>
            <li>• Preventing teeth from shifting</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      On-Site Fabrication Advantage
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">State-of-the-Art Equipment</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Our in-house dental laboratory allows us to create your dentures with precision and efficiency. 
            This means better quality control, faster turnaround times, and the ability to make adjustments 
            immediately when needed.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <span>Faster delivery - no waiting for external labs</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <span>Better quality control throughout the process</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <span>Immediate adjustments and repairs</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
              </div>
              <span>More cost-effective for patients</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Custom Fit & Comfort</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Every denture is custom-made to fit your unique mouth shape and bite. We take precise 
            impressions and measurements to ensure optimal comfort, function, and aesthetics.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-md">
            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">What Makes Our Dentures Special:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 text-sm">
              <li>• Precise digital impressions for perfect fit</li>
              <li>• Natural-looking teeth matched to your preferences</li>
              <li>• Comfortable, stable base design</li>
              <li>• Multiple try-in appointments for adjustments</li>
              <li>• High-quality, durable materials</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Denture Process
    </h2>

    <div class="grid gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Initial Consultation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Comprehensive examination of your mouth, discussion of your needs and expectations, 
              and explanation of denture options. We'll also address any necessary extractions or healing time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Impressions & Measurements</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We take detailed impressions of your mouth and measurements of your bite relationship. 
              These serve as the blueprint for creating your custom dentures.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-white font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-2">Try-In Appointment</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              You'll try on your dentures in a wax form to check fit, appearance, and bite. 
              We make any necessary adjustments to ensure you're completely satisfied before final processing.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-primary-900 font-bold">4</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Final Delivery</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Your completed dentures are delivered with instructions on care, cleaning, and what to expect 
              during the adjustment period. Follow-up appointments ensure optimal fit and comfort.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Caring for Your Dentures
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Daily Care</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Clean dentures daily with denture cleanser</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Soak overnight in denture solution</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Rinse after meals to remove food particles</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Brush your gums and remaining teeth</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Important Tips</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Handle carefully to avoid dropping and breaking</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Never use hot water (can warp the material)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Attend regular checkups for adjustments</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Start with soft foods during adjustment period</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Regain Your Smile & Confidence
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Don't let missing teeth hold you back from living your best life. Our custom-made dentures 
        can restore your ability to eat, speak, and smile with confidence.
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Denture Consultation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/dental-restoration" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Dental Implants</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Permanent tooth replacement option</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/extractions" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Tooth Extractions</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Removal before denture placement</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/crowns-bridges" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Crowns & Bridges</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Alternative restoration options</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How long does it take to get dentures?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        The denture process typically takes 4-6 weeks from start to finish. If extractions are needed, 
        healing time may extend this to 8-12 weeks. We can provide temporary dentures during the healing period.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Will I be able to eat normally with dentures?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Most patients adapt well to eating with dentures. Start with soft foods and gradually work up to 
        your regular diet. Well-fitted dentures allow you to enjoy most foods, though very hard or sticky 
        foods should be avoided.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How often do dentures need to be replaced?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Quality dentures typically last 5-7 years before needing replacement. However, they may need 
        periodic adjustments or relining as your mouth changes over time. Regular dental visits help 
        ensure optimal fit and function.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Are dentures covered by insurance?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Many dental insurance plans provide coverage for dentures, typically 50-80% after deductibles. 
        We'll help you understand your benefits and maximize your coverage. We also offer financing 
        options to make treatment affordable.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>